    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Synthetically prepared yellow iron oxide pigment having a medium to deep yellow color with good tinting strength. It is permanent, inexpensive, has good-film forming properties, acts as a drier for oil paints, and used extensively in the paint industry to produce cream tints with titanium dioxide.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047822/MFA Conservation and Art Material Encyclopedia Online: CAMEO (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種合成調製的黃色氧化鐵顏料，顏色為中黃至深黃，著色度優秀。馬爾斯黃為永久性顏料，價格不貴，又具能完好形成薄膜的特性，可當作油畫乾燥劑，並大量使用於油漆產業，與二氧化鈦相互作用形成奶油色。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
